eport-1773723889507.json\n/Users/wh1ko/.openclaw/skills/publish-geo/logs/debug-publish-1773725557766.png\n/Users/wh1ko/.openclaw/skills/publish-geo/logs/feishu-report-1773727968566.json\n/Users/wh1ko/.openclaw/skills/publish-geo/logs/feishu-report-1773725598952.json\n/Users/wh1ko/.openclaw/skills/publish-geo/logs/feishu-report-1773723770717.json\n/Users/wh1ko/.openclaw/skills/publish-geo/logs/debug-publish-1773730397985.png\n/Users/wh1ko/.openclaw/skills/publish-geo/logs/debug-publish-2-1773727961142.png"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":17,"aggregated":"/Users/wh1ko/.openclaw/skills/publish-geo/page-home.html\n/Users/wh1ko/.openclaw/skills/publish-geo/debug-2-publish.png\n/Users/wh1ko/.openclaw/skills/publish-geo/auth/bjh-work.json\n/Users/wh1ko/.openclaw/skills/publish-geo/articles/test-geo.md\n/Users/wh1ko/.openclaw/skills/publish-geo/README.md\n/Users/wh1ko/.openclaw/skills/publish-geo/page-source.html\n/Users/wh1ko/.openclaw/skills/publish-geo/logs/feishu-report-1773725415903.json\n/Users/wh1ko/.openclaw/skills/publish-geo/logs/debug-publish-2-1773727801965.png\n/Users/wh1ko/.openclaw/skills/publish-geo/logs/debug-success-1773728538581.png\n/Users/wh1ko/.openclaw/skills/publish-geo/logs/debug-publish-1773727951034.png\n/Users/wh1ko/.openclaw/skills/publish-geo/logs/feishu-report-1773723480252.json\n/Users/wh1ko/.openclaw/skills/publish-geo/logs/debug-publish-2-1773725725657.png\n/Users/wh1ko/.openclaw/skills/publish-geo/logs/feishu-report-1773728538670.json\n/Users/wh1ko/.openclaw/skills/publish-geo/logs/feishu-report-1773725728224.json\n/Users/wh1ko/.openclaw/skills/publish-geo/logs/debug-publish-2-1773728098414.png\n/Users/wh1ko/.openclaw/skills/publish-geo/logs/debug-publish-2-1773730408131.png\n/Users/wh1ko/.openclaw/skills/publish-geo/logs/debug-publish-2-1773725383882.png\n/Users/wh1ko/.openclaw/skills/publish-geo/logs/debug-publish-1773724909292.png\n/Users/wh1ko/.openclaw/skills/publish-geo/logs/debug-publish-2-1773724992911.png\n/Users/wh1ko/.openclaw/skills/publish-geo/logs/debug-publish-1773728824821.png\n/Users/wh1ko/.openclaw/skills/publish-geo/logs/debug-fail-1773724936529.png\n/Users/wh1ko/.openclaw/skills/publish-geo/logs/debug-publish-2-1773724069702.png\n/Users/wh1ko/.openclaw/skills/publish-geo/logs/debug-publish-1773723668840.png\n/Users/wh1ko/.openclaw/skills/publish-geo/logs/feishu-report-1773723889507.json\n/Users/wh1ko/.openclaw/skills/publish-geo/logs/debug-publish-1773725557766.png\n/Users/wh1ko/.openclaw/skills/publish-geo/logs/feishu-report-1773727968566.json\n/Users/wh1ko/.openclaw/skills/publish-geo/logs/feishu-report-1773725598952.json\n/Users/wh1ko/.openclaw/skills/publish-geo/logs/feishu-report-1773723770717.json\n/Users/wh1ko/.openclaw/skills/publish-geo/logs/debug-publish-1773730397985.png\n/Users/wh1ko/.openclaw/skills/publish-geo/logs/debug-publish-2-1773727961142.png","cwd":"/Users/wh1ko/Documents/openclaw/agents/writer"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1773751915281}}
